cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and acoustic modeling using deep neural networks. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speaker-dependent mappings for acoustic modeling. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a novel approach for speaker adaptive training using embeddings and control networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their application in speech recognition. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely as the paper does not deal with image or video data.
